<h3 id="installation">Installation</h3>

<p>Step 1. Download the file <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jhvanderschee/jekyllcodex/gh-pages/_includes/accordion.html">accordion.html</a>
<br />Step 2. Save the file in the â€˜_includesâ€™ directory of your project
<br />Step 3. Make sure your front matter of your page looks like the example above
<br />Step 4. Add the following line to your layout on the place where you want the form to appear:</p>

<pre><code>{% include accordion.html %}
</code></pre>
:ET